Nevertheless, since Nunberg’s monograph (Nunberg, 1990), the importance of the comma has been undeniable, mainly in these two as­ pects: i) as a due to the syntax of the sentence (Nunberg, 1990; Bayraktar et al., 1998; Garzia, 1997), and ii) as a basis to improve some natural language processing tools (syntactic analysers, error detection tools…), as well as to develop some new ones (Briscoe and Carroll, 1995; Jones, 1996).
